data.description: Need space at an affordable price? Look no further! At just under $116 per sq ft, this 2-story, 3 bedroom home has approx. 2,413 living square feet with beautiful bamboo hardwood flooring, brand new oversized ceiling fans, fresh paint, large functional kitchen island, great storage space, tons of cabinets and all appliances convey with the sale! Live the ideal cul-de-sac lifestyle you've always dreamed of in this established neighborhood near great shopping, recreation, schools, and so much more! All appliances convey. Seller offering $3,500 carpet allowance for upstairs bedrooms
